      <odd id="aspace_c5c7b3af4516b717e0241cfd5972929e">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-K-2 (YRG 13-K-2), Records of the Master of Saybrook College.</p>  
      </odd>
