      <scopecontent id="aspace_6d1d428aea97a5c6f265d977200be58f">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence concerning disciplinary actions and student recommendations of the master of Saybrook College.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_91d79212a128276d6018c5401f0ff1db">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The title "Master" for chief executive officers of residential colleges was changed to "Head of College" in April of 2016.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_c8637addb8d65670839ca0845ad67b4b">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
